  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.5.4">
<l>tāṉō ruruvē taṉivittāyt taṉṉiṉ mūvar mutalāya</l>
<l>vāṉōr palaru muṉivaru maṟṟu maṟṟu muṟṟumāy</l>
<l>tāṉōr perunīr taṉṉuḷḷē tōṟṟi yataṉuḷ kaṇvaḷarum</l>
<l>vāṉōr perumāṉ māmāyaṉ vaikun taṉem perumāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He is one form. Being a single seed, from that becoming many of the celestials</l>
<l>who have the Three as a beginning, sages, all the others and everything,</l>
<l>the lord of the celestials who made it appear on the great water, inside himself</l>
<l>[and] who sleeps in it, the great/dark trickster, the one from Vaikunta is our great lord.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
